2- Analyze the ratio of ratios (FINAL/BASAL TREATMENT BRANCH / FINAL/BASAL PLACEBO BRANCH) in both branches with their respective confidence intervals.

I can't find how to analyze option one with metagen, since I can only enter the TE and the seTE. I don't know if with this data the two branches could be analyzed directly in some way or directly with metafor.
